            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 7 月 8 日消息，三星将于&nbsp;7&nbsp;月&nbsp;9&nbsp;日（明天）在纽约市举办新&nbsp;Unpacked&nbsp;活动，不过目前消息源 Roland Quandt 已放出本次发布会大部分新品完整海报和参数信息，<strong>涉及 Galaxy Z Fold7&nbsp;、Galaxy Z Flip7 / FE、Galaxy Watch 8 Classic / Ultra 2025 等设备</strong>。</p><p>IT之家整理相应机型参数如下：</p><h3>三星&nbsp;Galaxy Z Fold7</h3><p>该机可选蓝 / 白 / 灰三种配色，展开厚度&nbsp;4.2mm，折叠厚度&nbsp;8.9mm，重量&nbsp;215g，外屏采用了一块&nbsp;6.5 英寸&nbsp;HD+&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;AMOLED 2X 面板，内屏采用了&nbsp;8&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;QXGA+&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;120Hz AMOLED 2X&nbsp;面板，提供&nbsp;10MP&nbsp;自拍摄像头。机身后置&nbsp;200MP&nbsp;主摄&nbsp;+ 12MP&nbsp;超广角&nbsp;+ 10MP&nbsp;长焦。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1297" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/e239e953-0428-418f-9485-f8580f8340ed.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="976" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1269" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/a2a6b3d8-0651-4094-ba5c-835102ee9cdb.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="1004" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="843" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/f9c32cad-d4ab-474b-bcf1-5f3276e97551.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="902" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/a50bcd41-74d7-4c95-997f-16fbb18fcb72.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="1400" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="760" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/84b6d1b6-2c91-4774-9a27-1ffe35e7f767.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="1440" /></p><p>该机搭载高通骁龙&nbsp;8&nbsp;至尊版&nbsp;For Galaxy&nbsp;处理器，匹配&nbsp;12GB / 16GB RAM&nbsp;和&nbsp;256GB / 512GB / 1TB&nbsp;存储空间，内置&nbsp;4400&nbsp;毫安时电池。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2000" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/eaa111ca-63e5-41b2-8129-b3cf83e93b47.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="759" /></p><h3>三星&nbsp;Galaxy Z Flip7</h3><p>该机可选蓝 / 黑 / 粉三种配色，展开厚度&nbsp;6.5mm，折叠厚度&nbsp;13.7mm，重量&nbsp;188&nbsp;克。外屏采用一块&nbsp;4.1&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;Super AMOLED&nbsp;面板，抛弃了“文件夹”式设计，内屏采用了一块&nbsp;6.9&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;FHD+ 120Hz AMOLED 2X&nbsp;面板，提供&nbsp;10MP&nbsp;自拍摄像头；机身后置&nbsp;50MP&nbsp;主摄和&nbsp;12MP&nbsp;超广角镜头。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1363" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/2b0f829e-81e8-4156-9193-6252ba24d93e.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="930" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1284" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/101d2dc0-7f13-44d9-a0ef-e08132f86bba.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="987" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1266" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/f7fee414-9c81-4420-b5ea-2ccddb14278a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="1000" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="785" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/7/5a5ddde8-ae17-48bc-9097-307b922e9dd2.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星新品海报参数大曝光：Galaxy Z Fold / Flip7 折叠屏手机、Watch8 / Ultra 2025 智能手表..." width="1440" /></p><p>该机搭载三星&nbsp;Exynos 2500&nbsp;处理器，匹配&nbsp;12GB RAM&nbsp;和&nbsp;256GB / 512GB&nbsp;存储空间，内置&nbsp;4300&nbsp;毫安时电池。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2000" src="https://img